



    <h1>Choose your Deck</h1>

     <p> Below are listed all the possible decks of flashcards you can choose from. Click on one to begin, or click your User Name to see your past progress.</p>

        <ul>
          <% @decks.each do |deck| %>
            <li><a href='/games/<%= deck.id %>'>
              <h3><%=  deck.name.capitalize %></h3></li></a>
